              "dialogueType": "sendNext",
              "text": "What? Neinheart sent you here? Ahh, you must be a rookie. Welcome, welcome. My name is Kiku, and my job is to train and mold kids like you into bonafide knights. Hmmm.. Why are you looking at me like that... Ahh, you must have never seen Piyos before."
            },
            "id": "start_0",
            "type": "dialogue"
          },
          {
            "dialogue": {
              "choices": [
