                },
                {
                  "nextState": null,
                  "text": "Exit"
                }
              ],
              "dialogueType": "sendNext",
              "text": "We belong to a race called Piyos. You've talked to Shinsoo before, right? The one that stands next to the Empress. Yeah, Shinsoo is a Piyo, too. He may be of a different class, but... oh well. Piyos are only found in Ereve, so you may find us a bit odd at first, but you'll get used to us."
