                {
                  "nextState": null,
                  "text": "Exit"
                }
              ],
              "dialogueType": "sendAcceptDecline",
              "text": "Ah, I don't know if you are aware of this, but you won't find any monsters here in Ereve. Any form of evil will not be able to set foot on this island. Don't worry, you'll still have your opportunity to train here. Shinsoo created a fantasy creature called Mimi, which will be used as your training partners. Shall we begin?"
